column2:
Base: Crafted from polished solid marble, offering stability and elegance.
Body: Chrome-plated metal stem with a sleek and curved design, complementing the contemporary style.
Shade: White fabric shade with a subtle geometric pattern, allowing soft and diffused light to pass through.
Light Source: Features a 10-watt LED bulb with adjustable color temperature, providing either bright illumination or ambient lighting as desired.
Control: Built-in touch switch on the base for easy operation, allowing you to turn the lamp on/off and adjust the light intensity effortlessly.
column3: Illuminate your home with elegance and style with our sophisticated table lamp. Its solid marble base exudes a sense of luxury and durability, while its chrome-plated metal stem adds a touch of modernity. The white fabric shade softens the light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere in any room. With its elegant design and versatile functionality, this table lamp is the perfect choice for adding a touch of sophistication to any space. Transform your home into a sanctuary of style and comfort with our exclusive table lamp.
